---

<section class="section-dark py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
      Take control of your bookmarks
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-[var(--color-dark-muted-foreground)]">
      Start with the hosted instance in seconds, or self-host with Docker.
      Every feature, every byte of data &mdash; your choice where it lives.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href="https://linkweave.dev/login"
        class="w-full rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-dark-primary)] px-6 py-3 text-center text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:brightness-110 sm:w-auto"
      >
        Launch LinkWeave &rarr;
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/linkweave/linkweave"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-dark-border)] bg-[var(--color-dark-card)] px-6 py-3 text-center text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-dark-foreground)] transition-all hover:bg-[var(--color-dark-secondary)] sm:w-auto"
      >
        View Source
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
